Fix #22?
Now the factorial example compiles to
```c
long factorial(long n) {
    {
        if (n == 0l)
            return 1l;
else
            return (n * factorial((n - 1l)));
}
    return 0l;
}

int main() {
    {
        display(factorial(5l));
}
    return 0l;
}
```

